              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Expert Insight</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <strong>Without professional coordination, expats often:</strong> Miss customs documents causing weeks of delays and storage fees, book moves without elevator access forcing manual carrying, underinsure valuable items leading to financial losses, forget parking permits resulting in fines and failed move-ins, or prepare pet documents incorrectly risking entry refusal. Expert moving logistics save time, money, and stress.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
