              <div class="ml-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">International Shipping & Customs Coordination</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                  Complete shipping management from origin to Switzerland including sea/air freight options, detailed inventory preparation for customs, Swiss customs clearance coordination, duty-free resident import processing, and tracking throughout transit.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Sea/Air Freight</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Customs Clearance</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Inventory Prep</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg">
                  2
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Building Access, Permits & Insurance</h3>
