                  Complete coordination with Swiss building management including elevator reservations, city parking permits for moving trucks (CHF 50-150), building liability insurance arrangement, access key coordination, and compliance with building move-in rules and timing restrictions.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Parking Permits</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Building Insurance</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Access Coordination</span>
                </div>
